{"id": 6940, "title": "Ticket #6940: event log and userlog times should have a year by default", "description": "<blockquote>\nNow that we have the capability to opt in to ISO_DATE and UTC for date and time in header line of userlog and event log, we should set the default to ISO_DATE.  We should delay setting this default until 8.8.2 has been in the wild for while, since that is the first version that will not choke on the new date format.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2019-Aug-12 11:54</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=57655\">[57655]</a></span>: version history for <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=6940\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6940'); return false;\" title=\"event log and userlog times should have a year by default\">#6940</a></span>.  (By John (TJ) Knoeller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2019-Jul-25 17:06</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=57497\">[57497]</a></span>: Fixed broken dagman test comparing logs with year vs no year (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=6940\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6940'); return false;\" title=\"event log and userlog times should have a year by default\">#6940</a></span>) Committer: Tim Theisen  (By Mark Coatsworth )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2019-Jul-18 13:41</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span